The active player rolls the dice until he gets a 1 or until he presses "Hold". 
The points he get by rolling the dice ads up on each other to the current score until he rolls a 1 or presses "Hold". 
If he rolls 1 all of the current score is lost and it's the next players turn, 
if the player presses "Hold" the points from current score are transfered to the main score and it's the next players turn. 
Points in the main score are also summarized from the current score. Goal of the Game is too reach 100 main points and press "Hold".
